==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Infilm
<hw>In*film"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cover with a
film; to coat thinly; <as>as, to <ex>infilm</ex> one metal with another
in the process of gilding; to <ex>infilm</ex> the glass of a
mirror.</as></def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

